 ───│    $Green├─┤│ │ │ │ │└─┐│  ├┬┘│├─┘ │   │  │ │ ├┤ $NC   │───
 ───│    $Green┴ ┴└─┘ ┴ └─┘└─┘└─┘┴└─┴┴   ┴   ┴─┘┴ ┴ └─┘$NC   │───
    │    ${YELLOW}Copyright${FONT} (C)$GRAY https://github.com/kytxz$NC     │
    └───────────────────────────────────────────────┘
         ${RED}Autoscript xray vpn lite (multi port)${FONT}    
${RED}Make sure the internet is smooth when installing the script${FONT}
        "
}
